So far,  Dr Godwin Maduka Foundation has distributed food stuff to 39 communities out of  181 communities in Anambra state. These communities make up four local Government Areas. The local government areas are Orumba South, Orumba North, Njikoka and Oyi. Therefore, Dr Godwin Maduka foundation has already given out food stuff to the needy in four(4) local Government Areas, remaining seventeen (17)Local Government Areas. Awgbu, Nanka, Oko, Ndiokpaleze, Ndiokaleke, Omogho, Amaetiti, Ndiukwuenu, and Okpeze towns received food stuff from the foundation on Thursday, 23rd April 2020. The remaining Communities will receive their package any moment from now as members of Dr Godwin Maduka foundation are not relenting in ensuring that food stuff gets to the needy in the entire state. 